reviewText:
Not exactly what I was expecting, but very good nonetheless. I was expecting a bigger world, tons of sidequests and all that makes a epic RPG game.

Pros:
- The world is beautifully drawn;
- The combat system is great;
- Workshop (I'll eventually come back because of it;
- The dialogs is very well detailed and well written;
- The music is very good;

Cons:
- There's not much to do besides the main quest;
- Checkpoint saves;
- Bad interface cleary designed for mobile devices;
- Basically no loot;
- No trade between characters;

Besides the cons, I enjoyed big time this game and will be back for the workshop. Recommended.
